description: This file defines a React functional component named Navbar, which renders a top navigation bar with brand information and action buttons, including a 'New Game' button that dispatches a 'new-game' custom event. It also imports an API client, but does not currently utilize it.

methods.name: Navbar()
methods.description: React functional component rendering the navigation bar with 'How it works' and 'New Game' buttons.

methods.name: onNewGame
methods.description: Event handler invoked when the 'New Game' button is clicked; dispatches a 'new-game' custom event.
